<item>
            <title>[KAFKA-1697] remove code related to ack&gt;1 on the broker</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-1697</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We removed the ack&amp;gt;1 support from the producer client in kafka-1555. We can completely remove the code in the broker that supports ack&amp;gt;1.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Also, we probably want to make NotEnoughReplicasAfterAppend a non-retriable exception and let the client decide what to do.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12747177">KAFKA-1697</key>
            <summary>remove code related to ack&gt;1 on the broker</summary>
